Tapi saya senior awak.

35
00:02:56,300 --> 00:02:57,400
Tak bolehkah?

36
00:02:59,070 --> 00:03:00,260
Tapi,

37
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,610
awak mentor saya,
