75
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,190
Tapi kami masih berkawan.

76
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,740
Seseorang yang ambil kesempatan
terhadap perasaan awak

77
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:26,380
