94
00:06:24,550 --> 00:06:25,520
Maksud awak?

95
00:06:25,610 --> 00:06:27,630
Jangan jawab panggilan dia

96
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,660
sehingga dia minta maaf.

97
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:31,590
Walaupun awak jawab,

98
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:34,280
jangan setuju untuk jumpa dia.

99
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:35,900
Tanpa kebenaran saya.

100
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,780
Macam mana kalau saya
terserempak dengan dia?

101
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,480
Koyak satu muka surat
dari buku Nam Soo-hyun.

102
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:47,960
Bukan senang nak buat begitu.

103
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,600
Ikut apa saya cakap.

104
