151
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,070
Kerja itu baguslah.

152
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,880
Jenis yang awak cari.

153
00:10:35,970 --> 00:10:38,470
Macam mana awak tahu?

154
00:10:39,490 --> 00:10:41,990
- Apa?
- Pekerjaan begitu tak pernah wujud.

155
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:44,190
Saya dengar yang

156
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:46,090
ada orang minta CEO buat pembukaan.

157
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:51,410
Patutlah ada bilik dan makanan,

158
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:54,270
