Saya cuma nak tolong awak.

175
00:11:46,410 --> 00:11:51,820
[Young-ran]

176
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:57,850
[Saya kata saya nak mati?]

177
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,830
Saya rasa awak selalu kata begitu

178
00:12:00,490 --> 00:12:02,600
